Annotation Interface Untransformed

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface Untransformed
Annotation which indicates that an inverse mapping function doesn't transform the value. A function which transforms the value can still be annotated as untransformed if the transform is guaranteed to lose no information or if it doesn't change the natural comparison order.
